sample_spec.max_tokens: set to max_output_tokens if provider specifies it. IF not set to max_tokens provider specifies
sample_spec.max_input_tokens: max input tokens, if the provider specifies it. if not default to max_tokens
sample_spec.max_output_tokens: max output tokens, if the provider specifies it. if not default to max_tokens
sample_spec.mode: one of chat, embedding, completion, image_generation, audio_transcription
